{"word":"H1168 - בַּעַל - Baʻal - bah'-al - Baal","slug":"H1168","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בַּעַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Baʻal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>bah'-al"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Baal"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>בּעל</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>ba‛al</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>bah'-al</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Baal = \"lord\" <ol><li>supreme male divinity of the Phoenicians or Canaanites (noun proper masculine)</li><li>a Reubenite (noun proper masculine)</li><li>the son of Jehiel and grandfather of Saul (noun proper masculine)</li><li>a town of Simeon, probably identical to Baalath-beer (noun proper locative)</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H1167\">H1167</a> <p />TWOT entry: <a class=\"T\" href=\"S:0262 - ba'al\">262a</a> <p />Part(s) of speech: "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1078\">H1078</a>, <a href=\"#/H1112\">H1112</a>, <a href=\"#/H1166\">H1166</a>, <a href=\"#/H1167\">H1167</a>, <a href=\"#/H1170\">H1170</a>, <a href=\"#/H1171\">H1171</a>, <a href=\"#/H1172\">H1172</a>, <a href=\"#/H1173\">H1173</a>, <a href=\"#/H1174\">H1174</a>, <a href=\"#/H1175\">H1175</a>, <a href=\"#/H1176\">H1176</a>, <a href=\"#/H1177\">H1177</a>, <a href=\"#/H1178\">H1178</a>, <a href=\"#/H1179\">H1179</a>, <a href=\"#/H1180\">H1180</a>, <a href=\"#/H1181\">H1181</a>, <a href=\"#/H1182\">H1182</a>, <a href=\"#/H1183\">H1183</a>, <a href=\"#/H1184\">H1184</a>, <a href=\"#/H1185\">H1185</a>, <a href=\"#/H1186\">H1186</a>, <a href=\"#/H1187\">H1187</a>, <a href=\"#/H1188\">H1188</a>, <a href=\"#/H1189\">H1189</a>, <a href=\"#/H1190\">H1190</a>, <a href=\"#/H1191\">H1191</a>, <a href=\"#/H1192\">H1192</a>, <a href=\"#/H1193\">H1193</a>, <a href=\"#/H1195\">H1195</a>, <a href=\"#/H1196\">H1196</a>"}]}